## Project Overview

This is a JavaScript RPG combat game with turn-based mechanics, featuring 4 hero classes (Mage, Warrior, Monk, Ninja) with unique abilities and progression system.

## Code Style

- Use Prettier for formatting (already configured)
- Follow JavaScript ES6+ standards
- Use camelCase for functions and variables
- Use kebab-case for CSS classes
- Use meaningful variable and function names
- Add comments for complex logic

## File Structure

- `/src/css/` - Stylesheets
- `/src/js/` - JavaScript logic
- `/src/assets/images/` - Game images
- `/src/data/` - JSON data files
- `/scripts/` - Utility scripts
- `/docs/` - Documentation

## Development Guidelines

- Always format code before committing
- Use the versioning system for releases
- Test functionality before pushing changes
- Update documentation when adding features
- Follow the existing code patterns

## Auto-formatting

- Format on save is enabled
- Use `npm run format` to format all files
- Use `npm run format:check` to check formatting
- Pre-commit hooks will auto-format code

## Version Control

- Use semantic versioning
- Update CHANGELOG.md for all changes
- Use conventional commit messages
- Run version scripts for releases
